The paper discusses a formal hybrid dynamical system model for building models of robots that make and break contact with their environment. This topic falls under the field of robotics, which is covered by the cs.RO sub-category. The paper also deals with modeling and control, which are covered by the cs.SY and cs.ME sub-categories. The use of mathematical models and formal reasoning suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the cs.AI and cs.LG sub-categories.
